              </li>
              <li class="list-group-item px-5">Theoretical training focuses on learning the traffic and cycling rules identifying dangerous situations.</li>
              <li class="list-group-item px-5">A detailed document for the student/commuter to navigate on the streets of Bangalore.</li>
              <li class="list-group-item px-5">The document also consists of questions back for the student to practise before the test.</li>
              <li class="list-group-item px-5">The document will be followed by an online test where their understanding of traffic rules will be tested. </li>
            </ul>
        </p>
