              </li> 
              <li class="list-group-item px-5">Practical training will prepare you for cycling on the road.</li>
              <li class="list-group-item px-5">Aimed at obtaining proper control over the cycle and learning how to manoeuvre in traffic.</li>
              <li class="list-group-item px-5">Practical training will be taught by a certified trainer or Instructor. </li>
              <li class="list-group-item px-5">The practical test will be organised and supervised by a certified instructor to ensure quality and safety.</li>
            </ul>
          </p>
