        <p class="lead mb-0">Is delivered on local roads giving trainees real cycling experience that equips them with skills to deal with traffic on short journeys such as cycling to school, work or the local shops.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-xs-12">
